Reasoning: 
1. cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper discusses the design of a DVB-S2 system to maximise spectrum efficiency, which involves information theory concepts such as channel variability and modulation schemes. 
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper focuses on satellite communication systems, which are a type of network architecture. 
3. cs.COMM (Computer Communications and Networks): The paper discusses the design of a communication system (DVB-S2) and proposes improvements to increase its efficiency. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a new design for the DVB-S2 system, which involves control and optimization of the system parameters. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper discusses the performance of the DVB-S2 system in transmitting multimedia content, which is the main application of the system.
